00:59:13,216 --> 00:59:14,877
# Hey ya, hey ya #

1016
00:59:14,984 --> 00:59:16,611
# And do you ever stop
to stare #

1017
00:59:16,719 --> 00:59:17,913
# Or take the time to care? #

